Class SMTExpr

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.smtlib.impl.SMTExpr
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAccept, IExpr, IPos.IPosable

    public abstract class SMTExpr
extends java.lang.Object
implements IExpr
    This class defines a number of subclasses that implement the SMT-LIB abstract AST; they are used by commands and expressions.
